   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Nourish Colombian children with vegetable gardens</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Colombia, 54.2% of families are nutritionally at risk. This means that more than half of Colombian families do not receive a minimum of three meals a day, nor the necessary nutrients to guarantee a healthy diet.   Together, we can create community, domestic and sustainable vegetable gardens that allow families to organize their own &quot;Food Encounters&quot; and thus have better access to fresh, nutritious and varied food.</narrative>
  </description>
